We are very excited to announce the availability of Terminaux 8.0, where we add more useful features to Terminaux and its components!

**Please note that the documentation will be released later than expected due to the amount of work that we have to refine the documentation.**

### Changes

This release contains a variety of changes, including, but not limited to:

- `[+]` Added audio cues
- `[+]` Added global password mask
- `[+]` Added a wide assortment of hidden commands
- `[+]` Added support for hidden commands
- `[+]` Added markdown export for commands
- `[+]` Added back specific VT sequence type getter
- `[*]` Improved redirection support
- `[*]` Performance improvements for string truncation
- `[*]` General improvements and bug fixes
- `[-]` Removed console checker

Review the commit history if you want to get a deep insight about the changes.

### Feedback?

If you have issues with this version, report to us by [making a new issue ticket](https://github.com/Aptivi/Terminaux/issues/new).

